reviewText: I bought two of these from Wholesale cable because I wanted short cables (less weight and bluk to carry around).  They actually measure 37.5 inch long from tip to tip (not 30 inch), and they're a little thicker than other USB cables I have, so they're not as compact as I'd hoped.  But they work and seem well made, which makes them a great deal for the price, so I gave them 5 star anyway.
